# Team Workflow

## Before coding
1. Find PRD story (`US-X.X`) in `docs/PRD.md`
2. Check `docs/TEAM_LOG.md` for overlapping work
3. Branch: `feature/US-X.X-short-description`

## While coding
- Smallest vertical slice: Prisma schema → migrate → service → route → test → UI
- Shared constants/errors → `packages/shared`
- New UI strings → `packages/i18n/locales/en.json` + `ar.json` (run `npm run lint:i18n`)

## Commits
```
type(scope): description
```
Types: `feat`, `fix`, `test`, `chore`, `docs`  
Scopes: `api`, `dashboard`, `pos`, `kds`, `agent`, `prisma`, `i18n`, `docker`

## After merging — update TEAM_LOG
Append to `docs/TEAM_LOG.md`:
```markdown
### YYYY-MM-DD — [Title]
**Phase:** N · **Story:** US-X.X (if any)
**What:** One-line summary
**Files:** key paths
**Verify:** commands or steps to test
**Notes:** breaking changes, env vars, migrations
```

## PR checklist
- [ ] Prisma migration included if schema changed
- [ ] `npm run lint` + `npm run lint:i18n` pass
- [ ] API tests pass (`npm run test -w @venue-pos/api`)
- [ ] `.env.example` updated if new env vars
- [ ] `TEAM_LOG.md` entry added
